/>

<!-- Overview -->
<section class="overview">
  <div class="ov-text">
    <div class="stag">The Service</div>
    <h2>One Team.<br />Total Scope.</h2>
    <p class="sdesc">
      A complete bathroom renovation involves eight distinct trades ‚Äî and coordinating
      them separately is a costly, stressful headache. We handle every stage under one
      contract, one price, and one point of contact. You choose the tiles, bathware,
      and tapware. We do everything else.
    </p>
    <div class="supply-split">
      <div class="supply-col we">
        <div class="supply-head">We Supply & Install</div>
        <ul>
          <li>All demolition labour & disposal</li>
          <li>Cement, sand, blocks for masonry</li>
          <li>All plumbing pipes and fittings</li>
          <li>Waterproofing membrane (walls + floor)</li>
          <li>Electrical conduit, wiring, fixtures</li>
          <li>Tile adhesive, grout, leveling clips</li>
          <li>Ceiling boards and fittings</li>
          <li>All labour for each trade</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="supply-col client">
        <div class="supply-head">You Supply</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Wall and floor tiles</li>
          <li>Bathware (toilet, basin, bathtub)</li>
          <li>Tapware (taps, shower head, mixers)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ov-price reveal">
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="pc-label">Starting From</div>
      <div class="pc-price">Rs. 15,000</div>
      <div class="pc-unit">per sq.ft ¬∑ all-inclusive</div>
      <div class="pc-note">Final price depends on bathroom size, existing condition, and scope of works. We provide a fixed quote after a free site visit.</div>
    </div>
    <a
      href="https://wa.me/94774503744?text=Hello%20TILERSHUB%2C%20I%20would%20like%20a%20bathroom%20renovation%20quote."
      class="quote-btn"
    >Get Bathroom Quote ‚Üí</a>
    <p class="price-note">Free site visit ¬∑ Fixed price quote ¬∑ No hidden charges</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Scope -->
<section class="scope">
  <div class="stag reveal">Full Scope Breakdown</div>
  <h2 class="reveal">Every Trade, Covered</h2>
  <p class="sdesc reveal">
    Eight trades, one team. Each stage is planned and sequenced so the project
    runs without delays between disciplines.
  </p>
  <div class="scope-grid reveal">
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">01</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üî®</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Demolition</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Complete removal of all existing fixtures, tiles, walls, and floor ‚Äî down to the structural substrate. Debris removed from site.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">02</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üß±</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Mason Work</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">New partition walls built, shower enclosure base formed, floor screed laid to correct falls for drainage. Structural work that everything else depends on.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">03</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üöø</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Plumbing</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Relocate or run new supply and drain lines, shower waste, floor drain, toilet soil pipe. All rough-in work completed and pressure-tested before walls close.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">04</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üíß</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Waterproofing</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Full membrane application to floor and walls of wet area ‚Äî applied in two coats with reinforcement tape at all junctions. The most critical stage for long-term performance.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">05</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">‚ö°</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Electrical</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Lighting circuit, exhaust fan wiring, shaver socket or heated towel rail circuit where specified. All IP-rated for wet area compliance.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">06</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üî≤</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Tiling</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Floor, all walls, shower enclosure ‚Äî fully tiled with a professional tile leveling system. Waterproof grout and silicone at all internal corners and junctions.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">07</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üè†</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Ceiling</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">Moisture-resistant ceiling board installed, taped and set, ready for paint or ceiling tile. Exhaust fan and light fittings cut in and installed.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-card">
      <div class="sc-num">08</div>
      <div class="sc-icon">üö™</div>
      <div class="sc-name">Fixtures & Shower Cubicle</div>
      <div class="sc-desc">All client-supplied bathware and tapware installed: toilet, basin, taps, shower head, mixers, shower cubicle, accessories. Final checks and handover.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why One Team -->
<section class="why">
  <div class="stag reveal">Why One Team</div>
  <h2 class="reveal">The Advantage of<br />Single-Contract Renovation</h2>
  <div class="reasons reveal">
    <div class="reason">
      <div class="r-num">01</div>
      <div class="r-name">No Coordination Gaps</div>
      <div class="r-desc">When all trades are under one contract, the plumber and tiler talk to each other ‚Äî not through you. Sequencing is managed internally.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="reason">
      <div class="r-num">02</div>
      <div class="r-name">Fixed Price Contract</div>
      <div class="r-desc">One quote covers every trade. There are no surprise add-ons when the electrician discovers what the plumber left behind.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="reason">
      <div class="r-num">03</div>
      <div class="r-name">Single Accountability</div>
      <div class="r-desc">One team is responsible for the finished result ‚Äî no blaming another trade for a problem. We own the outcome.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="reason">
      <div class="r-num">04</div>
      <div class="r-name">Faster Project</div>
      <div class="r-desc">Trades are mobilised consecutively without waiting periods between contractors. A typical bathroom renovation runs 10‚Äì14 working days.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Timeline -->
